curl http://0.0.0.0:3000/

Insert or login an user
curl -d '{"name":"pan"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/session
curl -d '{"name":"zoppo"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/session
curl -d '{"name":"fraffolo"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/session

NO
curl --user pan:pan182 -d '{"name":"panJson"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles?username=punk

Modifica username
curl http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles?username=pan -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer pan182" -d '{"name":"newPanNickname"}'
curl -d '{"name":"newPanNickname"}' -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer pan182" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles/pan
curl -X PUT -d '{"name":"newpan"}' -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer ghsr20230404131612" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles/pan

per vedere header di risposta
curl -i --user pan:pan182 -d '{"name":"newPanNickname"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles?userid=pan

curl -d '{"name":"pan"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles?userid=punk

Authorization test
curl -i http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles?username=pan -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer pan164" -d '{"name":"fraffolo"}'

Run application
go run ./cmd/webapi/.

Upload a photo
curl -X POST --data @image.txt -H "Authorization: Baerer mspv20230322163441" http://localhost:3000/profiles/pan/photos

Delete a photo
curl -X DELETE -H "Authorization: Baerer gxmt20230330184949" http://localhost:3000/profiles/pan/photos/gxmt20230331142500

Follow an user
curl -d '{"name":"zoppo"}' -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer gxmt20230330184949" http://0.0.0.0:3000/follows

Unfollow an user
curl -X DELETE -H "Accept: application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer rwuc20230328131133" http://0.0.0.0:3000/profiles/pan/follows/zoppo

Like a photo
curl -X POST -H "Authorization: Baerer jqux20230328130421" http://localhost:3000/photos/jqux20230329184759/likes

Comment a photo
curl -d '{"comment":"wow!"}' -H "Content-type:application/json" -H "Authorization: Baerer rwuc20230328131133" http://0.0.0.0:3000/photos/jqux20230329184759/comments

Get a photo
curl -X GET --output test.png -H "Authorization: Baerer aiai20230404131621" http://0.0.0.0:3000/photos/ghsr20230405100110
